  "sections": {
    "overview": {
      "heading": "業務簡介",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "segments": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "材料-KY (4763，Jinan Acetate Chemical) 為全球醋酸纖維絲束 (用於香菸濾嘴) 及醋酸纖維素製造商，營運總部位於中國濟南。垂直整合從醋酮至醋酐至醋酸片至絲束全製程，子公司"
            },
            {
              "type": "wikilink",
              "text": "孟玄新材料"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "自製醋酐。全球絲束市場為寡占結構，"
            },
            {
              "type": "wikilink",
              "text": "Celanese"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " (38%)、"
            },
            {
              "type": "wikilink",
              "text": "Eastman"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " (25%)、"
            },
            {
              "type": "wikilink",
              "text": "Daicel"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " (19%)、Blackstone (15%) 主導，公司市佔約 2% 目標 5%。下游客戶涵蓋全球四大菸草集團 — "
            },
            {
              "type": "wikilink",
              "text": "Philip Morris International"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "、"
            },
            {
              "type": "wikilink",
              "text": "British American Tobacco"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "、"
            },
            {
              "type": "wikilink",
              "text": "Japan Tobacco International"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "、"
            },
            {
              "type": "wikilink",
              "text": "Imperial Brands"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "及"
            },
            {
              "type": "wikilink",
              "text": "台灣菸酒"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "。亦服務"
            },
            {
              "type": "wikilink",
              "text": "IQOS"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "加熱菸市場。毛利率約 63%。"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
